About
=============================================

Here are some rpm spec files for various software and small utility scripts and so on.


rpm spec files (*.spec)
=============================================

You may build srpms from these rpm spec files with using buildsrpm.sh in this repo like this:

  ssato@localhost% ./buildsrpm.sh python-xlutils.spec /tmp
  [Info] Found the url of source in source0: 'http://pypi.python.org/packages/source/x/xlutils/xlutils-1.5.1.tar.gz'
  [Info] Try downloading the source ... Done
  書き込み完了: /tmp/python-xlutils-1.5.1-1.fc16.src.rpm
  ssato@localhost%


Requirements: rpm-build, curl, rpm-python

